replyContent:
Hi Thomas- 

We use the https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mersenne_Twister 19937 algorithm with a device specific source of entropy to randomize our games. The difficulty does not increase with proficiency - you've likely just hit a streak of difficult games!
